fields.title: Hello kitty dress for LittleFee and Volks yosd
fields.description:
Hello kitty dress for LittleFee, Volks yosd and or the same size doll.

Dress are made of American cotton. 
All seams are processed on overlock, fastened on the back with snaps.

Doll and props are not included!

This outfit will fit LittleFee and other similar sized dolls.
Dress is modeled by FairyLand LittleFee Ante. 

Thank you for looking)))

fields.title: Set for LittleFee and Volks yosd
fields.description:
Cute set for LittleFee, Volks yosd and or the same size doll.

The set is sewn from cotton Jersey. Hoodie with a hood and a snaps closure (Snaps on the back).
Striped socks made of cotton jersey.
Bloomers are made of American cotton.

In the set is included: 
- Hoodie
- Bloomers 
- Striped socks

Doll and props are not included!

This outfit will fit LittleFee and other similar sized dolls.
Dress is modeled by FairyLand LittleFee Ante. 

Thank you for looking)))
